        <task>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    <em>Requirements:</em> <m>f(6)=0</m>, <m>\displaystyle\lim_{x\to6 } f(x)=-2</m>, <m>\displaystyle\lim_{x\to-2^-}f(x)=1</m>, and <m>\displaystyle\lim_{x\to -2} f(x)</m> does not exist.
